Two possible strategies to reduce the nesting here:

Negate all of the conditions, and "return early," e.g.:

if (!currentCondition) {
    return;
}
// This code is now left by four columns

Add a helper method, where you can perform all of these checks in one place.

if (!validUpdate(...)) {
    return;
}
// This code is now left by 4 * k columns

